text: Malaprabha Jadhav is an Indian Kurash wrestler and a Judo Player. In 2018 Asian Games, at Jakarta in 52 kg she won a bronze medal. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Kurash practitioners at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games medalists in kurash Category:Asian Games bronze medalists for India Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:21st-century Indian women Category:1998 births
